# Version and changelog (many_faces_redis)

**Before `git commit`** on any user-visible **feature**, **fix**, or behaviour change in **`many_faces_redis`**, update **`CHANGELOG.md`** and **`VERSION`**. Include both in the **same commit** as the code change.

## Steps (before commit)

1. Add bullet(s) under `## [Unreleased]` — `### Added`, `### Changed`, or `### Fixed` (English, no dates in headings).
2. Run **`./scripts/bump-version.sh minor`** (feature) or **`patch`** (fix/docs-only).
3. Run **`./scripts/verify-version-files.sh`**.
4. Stage `VERSION`, `CHANGELOG.md`, and feature files together.

## Skip

- Question-only turns; typo-only edits (optional patch; user may waive).

## Monorepo

When the monorepo bumps this submodule pointer, the root [`many_faces_main`](https://github.com/01laky/many_faces_main) stack version is updated separately — see its [`CHANGELOG.md`](https://github.com/01laky/many_faces_main/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md).
